Commands for managing Frappe apps in the current project.

Examples:
  weg app list              # List installed apps
  weg app get <url>         # Install an app
  weg app remove <name>     # Remove an app
  weg app switch <branch>   # Switch app branch

Usage:
  app [command]

Available Commands:
  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
  exclude     Exclude an app from sync
  get         Install an app
  help        Help about any command
  include     Include an excluded app
  list        List apps in the project
  reinstall   Reinstall an app (uninstall + install)
  remove      Remove an app
  switch      Switch an app to a different branch

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for app

Use "app [command] --help" for more information about a command.
